notes.title: Availability of data and materials
notes.p: With the permission of the corresponding authors, we can provide participant data without names and identifiers but not the study protocol, statistical analysis plan, or informed consent form. Data can be provided after the Article is published. Once the data can be made public, the research team will provide an email address for communication. The corresponding authors have the right to decide whether to share the data based on the research objectives and plan provided.
